{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"1dad2861-a958-4f8b-a855-26df64be0411","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest compatibility bridge by default.**\n\nIn 3.x, even though `Microsoft.Testing.Platform` was enabled, the VSTest adapter bridge was still bundled so `vstest.console` could discover and run tests. In 4.x, that bridge is no longer included, which is why `vstest.console` sees zero tests.\n\n### You have two options\n\n**Option A – Switch your CI to `dotnet test` (recommended)**\n\n`dotnet test` works natively with Microsoft.Testing.Platform. No project changes needed:\n\n```\ndotnet test TestProject.csproj\n```\n\n**Option B – Re-enable the VSTest bridge**\n\nIf you must keep `vstest.console`, add this property:\n\n```xml\n<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>\n```\n\nWant me to update your `.csproj` with Option B?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"54f202d7-86b9-4941-8556-dff9103f56a4","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest SDK. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.8.0 (or around that version), MSTest began transitioning from the VSTest runner to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP). In MSTest.Sdk 4.x, the VSTest compatibility layer was removed by default.\n\nSpecifically, in MSTest.Sdk 3.x, the `EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform` property defaulted to `true` but the VSTest adapter/compatibility was still included. In MSTest.Sdk 4.x, the VSTest compatibility bridge is no longer included by default, so `vstest.console` can't discover tests.\n\n\nThere are two ways to resolve this: either migrate the CI pipeline to use `dotnet test` instead, which works natively with Microsoft.Testing.Platform, or add the `EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge` property set to `true` in the project file to restore VSTest compatibility. The core issue is that MSTest.Sdk 4.0+ dropped the VSTest bridge by default, requiring one of these adjustments to maintain backward compatibility with `vstest.console`.","outputTokens":550,"requestId":"7C21:1EA0BA:187F998:1BE8078:69F9602D"},"id":"91077980-f859-466e-89fe-e6e94d2d2f55","timestamp":"2026-05-05T03:12:56.260Z","parentId":"6e1e9f83-95e6-4e76-9606-a084b5072ff7"}
